      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously cared for in a climate-controlled environment, with every service record accounted for and performed on schedule. The engine runs flawlessly with plenty of power, the transmission shifts are imperceptibly smooth, and the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch or swirl mark. Inside, the leather remains supple and free of wear, and all electronic features and driver aids function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and drives like new.",
