    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and remains linear all the way to the 8,000 RPM redline. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and reinforcement of the rear subframe floor to ensure longitudinal rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts crisply, and the variable M differential lock provides excellent traction out of corners. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, offering the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use, the drivetrain and cooling system are in peak operating condition, making this an ideal driver-focused example.",
